{"tid":628924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"DSE英文科蜜蜂題　讀生物或有利","createTime":"2018-04-14T09:32:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T09:35:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"88ffcc33d19f075719aef75ed079451bdd1f92b3","tid":628924,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T09:32:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180414/20361318?_ga=2.12200756.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180414%2F20361318%3F_ga%3D2.12200756.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=y2KIXyCTZjw%2B5kY2bIgPD5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=295a1292\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180414%2F20361318%3F_ga%3D2.12200756.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=393d1aab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180414/20361318?_ga=2.12200756.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\nDSE英文科蜜蜂題　讀生物或有利<br />\n<br />\n7.3K<br />\n港聞<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180414/large/0413catony2007.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180414%2Flarge%2F0413catony2007.jpg&h=746adae0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄧美儀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中學文憑試主科考試，廠商會中學英文科主任鄧美儀指昨開考的英文科卷一閱讀較去年淺，尤其必答的A部份，以及供能力較低同學選答的B1部份，長題目數量較去年少。另卷一的閱讀篇章均圍繞蜜蜂，較多深字跟生物科有關，以英文修讀生物的考生或有利。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n考模仿班主任寫通告<br />\n<br />\n至於卷二作文，第一部份要求考生以班主任身份，向家長寫通告講解學生即將前往「Sky 100」旅行的行程，鄧稱近年沒出過類似題目，但課程有相關訓練，只要考生注意「班主任」的用字及語調，不難應付。<br />\n<br />\n相反，巧妙的題目在於第二部份，考生須在8條題目中選答1題寫作400字，鄧認為第4題「看似」最淺，題目要求考生以雜誌專欄作者身份，回建議信予一位想成為獸醫但父母反對的16歲年輕人。應屆考生葉同學選答此題，坦言發揮空間一般，僅建議對方多找相關課程資料，又建議與父母面對面傾談。<br />\n<br />\n鄧解釋上述題目看似容易，但題目歸類為「social issue」而非「workplace」，料不可只針對獸醫這職業作討論，或要探討時下家庭的親子關係。<br />\n<br />\n■記者周　婷"},{"pid":"c05658d4e2ad261f26e284ce38da7986ed0b32d8","tid":628924,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T09:35:54.000Z","msg":"樓主硬膠泛民打手LIKLN<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=3124d977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ff15f2d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/10/201929_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F10%2F201929_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=27225035&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}